column3: to be taught. to learn. to take lessons in.
closing. ending before one had the time to do something one wanted to do.
to relax. to make oneself comfortable.
to be silent. to say nothing.
to bear a grudge against. to resent. to blame.
to bring down. to fell. to knock something down.
to leave alone. to leave as is. to ignore. to neglect.
implies you think something is garbage.
being extremely busy. being swamped with work.

column2: こうさいいしょくしょう
